                  <div class="mb-1">Auto-discovered Azure URL (NEVER overridden). Always shows the actual provisioned endpoint.</div>
                  <div class="text-xs mt-1">Examples: <code class="px-1 bg-white dark:bg-neutral-700 rounded">https://myapp.azurewebsites.net</code>, <code class="px-1 bg-white dark:bg-neutral-700 rounded">https://myapi.azurecontainerapps.io</code></div>
