                  <div class="text-xs mt-1">Examples: <code class="px-1 bg-white dark:bg-neutral-700 rounded">https://www.contoso.com</code>, <code class="px-1 bg-white dark:bg-neutral-700 rounded">https://api.fabrikam.com/v1</code></div>
