                  <div class="mb-1">Custom domain name for Azure deployment (domain only, no protocol). Converted to HTTPS URL for display. The original Azure URL is preserved in <code class="px-1 bg-white dark:bg-neutral-700 rounded">azure.url</code>.</div>
                  <div class="text-xs mt-1">Can be auto-discovered from Azure resource settings (e.g., App Service custom domain) or set locally in azure.yaml.</div>
                  <div class="text-xs mt-1">Examples: <code class="px-1 bg-white dark:bg-neutral-700 rounded">www.contoso.com</code>, <code class="px-1 bg-white dark:bg-neutral-700 rounded">api.fabrikam.com</code></div>
