          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-300">
            <li><strong>CLI (<code class="px-1 bg-white dark:bg-neutral-800 rounded">azd app info</code>):</strong> Shows both "Access URL" (custom) and original URL when they differ</li>
            <li><strong>Dashboard:</strong> Primary link uses the custom URL; hover/tooltip shows the original provisioned URL</li>
            <li><strong>Service Discovery:</strong> Environment variables reference the appropriate URL based on context</li>
